00:22:22,574 --> 00:22:24,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya perlu membuat kertas Goryeo.</font>

292
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:27,635
<font color=#FFFF00>Kertas Goryeo Unpyeongsa.</font>

293
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,563
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku minta maaf...</font>

294
