<font color=#FFFF00>Aku minta maaf...</font>

295
00:23:03,434 --> 00:23:04,736
<font color=#FFFF00>Selama ini...</font>

296
00:23:05,966 --> 00:23:08,532
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kamu menanggungnya sendirian?</font>

297
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:16,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa hidup karena pengorbananmu.</font>

298
00:23:17,538 --> 00:23:19,686
